org.fcrepo.client.utility.validate.remote

Class TypeUtility

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fcrepo.client.utility.validate.remote.TypeUtility

  • public class TypeUtility
extends Object
    A collection of utility methods for converting between local objects and those that are generated by the WSDL-based API-M and API-A clients.
    Author:
    Jim Blake
